Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:20.80,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}哼唱的旋律 勾起無盡的思緒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.80,0:00:24.69,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塵封的記憶 閃耀刺眼的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:28.62,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta remember　現在的你仍握有夢的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.62,0:00:32.82,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那時一樣 綻放光芒吧 少年的情懷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:34.82,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在欄杆上刻下將來的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:36.96,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時起我經歷了多少滄桑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.96,0:00:38.87,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在現實與理想的夾縫中搖擺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:41.09,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱情的火焰也已燃燒殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.09,0:00:42.87,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等! 我說等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.87,0:00:45.08,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺起胸膛 勝負才剛剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.08,0:00:47.13,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄的時候就是遊戲結束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:49.28,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的雙手打破現狀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:50.07,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起來了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:53.30,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們曾為了一線希望而全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.30,0:00:55.24,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了明天而努力生存
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.24,0:00:57.30,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的心情已經忘記了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:00:58.98,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春沒有極限
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:01.99,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇心和年齡無關 我是這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.99,0:01:03.12,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:05.60,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We wanna make the fream come true　所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:09.53,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綻放吧 綻放吧 綻放吧 熱情之花綻放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.53,0:01:12.73,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綻放吧 綻放吧 綻放吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.73,0:01:17.57,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼唱的旋律勾起無盡的思緒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.57,0:01:21.73,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塵封的記憶閃耀刺眼的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.73,0:01:25.57,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta remember　現在的你仍握有夢的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.57,0:01:30.47,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}就像那時一樣 綻放光芒吧少年的情懷
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.37,0:22:25.77,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}想要真心喜歡上一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.77,0:22:29.82,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻在害怕內心受到傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.82,0:22:33.93,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明自己什麼也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.93,0:22:37.17,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻只是說出逞強的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.17,0:22:45.19,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏於內心的軟弱 我視而不見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.19,0:22:50.23,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連那種事情 也能輕易驅散的巨大的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:54.26,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於找到了　You are my sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.26,0:22:58.37,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fly away Fly away　如果和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.37,0:23:02.47,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fly away Fly away　就不會感到害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.47,0:23:06.33,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fly away Fly away　即使失敗也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.33,0:23:10.21,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go another place　Take it easy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.21,0:23:14.47,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fly away Fly away　讓我飛上藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.47,0:23:18.66,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fly away Fly away　不再感到迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:22.55,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fly away Fly away　這都是因為有你在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.55,0:23:28.41,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1500)}Take my chance　Believe in myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.29,0:23:45.02,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Take it easy
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反射膜修得怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光粒子泉乾涸的狀態下 修理進展很慢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.70,0:01:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們到底要在這兒窩到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的混著沙子的飯菜我已經吃膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.50,0:01:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去恐怕要花上一年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去聯繫一下反射膜職人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.00,0:02:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們不是和軍隊有關係麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能暗地裏給我們做麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼哈普恐怕又要愁眉苦臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 一共需要幾張反射膜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少276張
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼多 那得多少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概要…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別算了 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單來說我們現在沒錢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.40,0:02:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為月光號不能飛 所以沒法接活兒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不幹活兒但誰也沒少吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之錢是單方面減少
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但總也不能就這麼在這兒等著它自己長好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當成是先期投資
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:02:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時取消化妝品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月光號現在進入第5戰斗配置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說進入缺錢模式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Skyrock Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫你拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許你碰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之別靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我頭疼 今天就讓我休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼 優萊卡身體不好 你來駕駛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:03:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向來小心的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆出什麼事了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為你們是純潔的一對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說大聲點 風聲很吵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道為什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是知道我就不用犯愁了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩的心就像秋天的天空啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是秋天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 這是老話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險 小心點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是接近過科拉利安麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就從那之前開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有點偏離軌道 優萊卡和我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之前一直很好麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是吧 總之還挺投緣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春真是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼樣 推倒了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那接吻總有過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 連這都沒有麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人要主動進攻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈普 通信器一直開著麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是麼 哎呀 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓 男人就是要進攻進攻再進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話讓只會跟在希爾德\N屁股後面轉的人說出來可沒什麽説服力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那叫男人的包容心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂包容心就是成天跟人認錯道歉麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之一句話 女孩的心就像秋天的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這剛才聽你說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人別為小事斤斤計較
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得 咱們一起也這麼長時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是對於你 對於你的心情 我卻一點都不瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想更多地瞭解你 因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 抱歉 光顧著睡 有事麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希爾德找你 叫你幫忙洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 接下來該疊衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 看好 襪子要像這樣折成三疊 然後張開 這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 嗯 這樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 讓我來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我自己來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近你是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麽這麽問
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:08:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你竟然自己不去開尼爾瓦修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不想開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為尼爾瓦修心情不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果蘭頓不在 我就開不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得呢 把尼爾瓦修看成你的女朋友倒是很合適
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經和自己很要好的女孩找到了男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎的跟這個女孩總會鬧點別扭不是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得好像自己的朋友被那男朋友搶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在吃醋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃醋?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這種表情 就像從來沒有過似的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候真是搞不懂你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你還是應該好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是在吃誰的醋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是尼爾瓦修呢還是蘭頓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疊好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也疊好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算這樣呆到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候? 你不喜歡跟我獨處麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知我問的不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是存心逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是無可奈何吧 月光號現在這副樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼辦 修好以後怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修好以後你又準備逃到哪兒去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.20,0:09:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是挖掘業者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:10:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信這裡還有礦脈 認為這裡的某處一定埋藏著夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好悲傷的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃德蒙德在麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.50,0:10:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃德蒙德不在麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經停業了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃德蒙德 是我 肯戈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃德蒙德死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然一大早就喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喝酒花的是自己的錢 你有意見麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.20,0:11:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適可而止吧 尼爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 你知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 你們是討債的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要反射膜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說我們是來買反射膜的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為你要說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東西我已經不幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又費事又沒銷路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是來訂貨的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.40,0:11:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了我不做這種狗屁活兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.80,0:11:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊 莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒出息 這是埃德蒙德的兒子該說的話麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:12:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙可是在製作反射膜上傾注了全部的熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可結果怎麼樣 一貧如洗 結果患上了絕望病死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕望病…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢我們有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 還沒還價啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工人們都跑光了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.30,0:12:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是來收貨的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過機器已經很久沒用過了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怕麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這什麼意思 我再怎麼喝酒這手藝可是沒落下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓我們見識見識你這手藝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成交
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:13:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 喝點酒才好幹活兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝成這樣不要緊麼 當初我確實這麼想過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看見了 奧拉德彭特山谷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是有一點點光粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要去飛魚聚集的場所嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是等它們聚集 是我們想辦法讓它們聚集
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有音樂好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 就只有這種啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著這種音樂我就想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就喝酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝酒會好些麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少你就搞不清弄得你想吐的是音樂還是酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死 喝就喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 再多喝點 再多喝點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給蒙多吉那小子喝了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏龍茶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.00,0:14:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏龍茶?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人們開始喝酒狂歡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照尼爾的說法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:15:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛魚會飛到魂魄驅動器邊上的快樂的人身邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真是這樣麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喝得還不夠多 這點程度的話飛魚會飛走的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來表演我的第36种絕活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餃子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 再多喝點 熱烈點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺純粹是在胡來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼沒什麼啊 你最近狀態不好不是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們也很擔心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們好像在躲著我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是自然的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.20,0:16:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也不會接近悶悶不樂的人的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微笑微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喝啊喝啊 怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要多想快樂的事就好了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:16:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別停下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 大家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站不起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別胡說 好戲這才要開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 用滑空板壓住它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆在那兒別動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別發呆 小心後面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:17:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:17:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先捉一隻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 我們努力收集了不少飛魚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣搬到工作室去就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不過接下去就是我一個人的活兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人很辛苦的吧 我們也幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專家的工作用不著外行插手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是想幫忙的話 就處理下那宴會的殘局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專家的工作麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這讓我想起了爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼爾也是個職人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當晚 尼爾的工作室的燈光一直沒有熄滅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除去轉去地方軍的7人 全員到齊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很感謝你們一直以來的暗中支持
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們等這一天很久了 中校…不 聽說您晉升上校了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是個虛名 無聊陳腐的老規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前幾天的預算委員會 正式批准了部隊的重組
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前雖然只有上校和我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但相信幾天之內各位就會接到轉屬命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下終於…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:19:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊 無聊透頂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢人會議至今仍不瞭解其真意麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是給出這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就足夠讓那些半吊子的學者折騰了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們存在的社會就是如此淺薄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.50,0:20:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,始終堅定不移地相信自己就是正義的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都該去死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要揭穿這社會的虛偽 掌握世界的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人類再次以主人的身份君臨這星球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成英雄阿德洛克·薩斯頓的未竟事業
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 就是第二次愛之夏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.80,0:20:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 最後的一批也固定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:20:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.10,0:20:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃德蒙德也會為你驕傲的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸要是還在的話 這會兒一定會踹我的屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.90,0:21:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 總算最後做了一次漂亮活兒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要關門了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.30,0:21:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別誤會 要是能繼續我也想繼續 可是沒生意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊不是你的主顧麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年開始忽然不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下就能修理了 快搬進去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過一想到是用飛魚做的 就總覺得有點可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:22:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…不過 很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.30,0:22:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候 我覺得和優萊卡的關係似乎有所恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待續
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.10,0:23:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在發掘現場遇到的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.20,0:23:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年在他身上看見了父親的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.90,0:23:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被夢想出賣的人所展現的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.60,0:23:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓少年領悟到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.10,0:24:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 Ill Communication


